<div id="content" class="content wikipage" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p id="l1">
A type of graphic arts <a title="Process Camera" href="Process_Camera">process camera</a> in which the <a title="Copyboard" href="Copyboard">copyboard</a>, <a title="Lens" href="Lens">lens</a>, and <a title="filmboard" class="nonexistent" href="http://printwiki.org/filmboard">filmboard</a> are aligned in a vertical plane, as opposed to a <a title="Horizontal Camera" href="Horizontal_Camera">horizontal camera</a>. See <a title="Photography: Graphic Arts Photography" class="nonexistent" href="http://printwiki.org/Photography:_Graphic_Arts_Photography">Photography: Graphic Arts Photography</a>. 
</p>
